---
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Test
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:3333
paths:
  '/test':
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              additionalProperties: false
              properties:
                email:
                  type: string
                scopes:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    type: string
              required:
                - email
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A Test Object
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: A Test Object
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/test": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/html]
